---
title: Carb Smart Crispy Dal-Coated Paneer with Clementine and Creamy Mint Dressing
description: The warming, mild heat of our curry paste gives pan-fried paneer loads of flavour, while crispy chana dal adds a delightful crunch. The cooling mint dressing brings a creamy freshness!

